io.spine.server.aggregate

Class EventImportDispatcher<I>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.aggregate.EventImportDispatcher<I>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of aggregate IDs
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.spine.logging.Logging, MessageDispatcher<io.spine.core.EventClass,io.spine.core.EventEnvelope,java.util.Set<I>>, MulticastDispatcher<io.spine.core.EventClass,io.spine.core.EventEnvelope,I>, EventDispatcher<I>, ExternalDispatcherFactory<I>

    @Internal
public final class EventImportDispatcher<I>
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventDispatcher<I>, io.spine.logging.Logging
    Dispatches events to be imported to the associated aggregate repository.
    API Note:
    This internal class is made public for restricting types of dispatchers that can be registered with an ImportBus. Since only Aggregate Repositories can dispatch imported events to their aggregates, we limit the type of the import event dispatches to this class, which neither can be extended, nor created from outside of this package. Instances of this class are proxies that Aggregate Repositories create and register with an ImportBus of their parent Bounded Context.
